00:12:10.206 --> 00:12:13.648
covenant family on Kipurym so that we can

00:12:13.687 --> 00:12:15.587
camp out together during Sukah.

00:12:16.567 --> 00:12:17.128
Thus far,

00:12:17.207 --> 00:12:19.489
Yahowah has made it abundantly clear that

00:12:19.548 --> 00:12:23.710
he isn't ambivalent about how we respond

00:12:23.750 --> 00:12:24.169
to him.

00:12:24.970 --> 00:12:27.791
Those who rely upon him will be protected

00:12:27.910 --> 00:12:29.971
and they will ultimately triumph.

00:12:31.109 --> 00:12:33.311
We have previously considered Yahowah's

00:12:33.350 --> 00:12:36.092
presentation of the Mow'ed Miqra'ey of Pesach

00:12:36.113 --> 00:12:37.033
and Matsah, of course,

00:12:37.094 --> 00:12:38.875
in our opening programs.

00:12:38.936 --> 00:12:40.576
And here we are now considering the

00:12:40.618 --> 00:12:41.938
implications of Bikuwrym,

00:12:41.999 --> 00:12:42.980
the firstborn children.

00:12:43.700 --> 00:12:47.143
And so as we move into another statement

00:12:47.202 --> 00:12:50.826
that Yahowah has to offer to explain the

00:12:50.907 --> 00:12:54.889
purpose of Bikuwrym, He has this to say.

00:12:55.931 --> 00:12:58.792
Then Yahowah spoke these words to Moshe in

00:12:58.851 --> 00:13:00.393
order to promise and say,

00:13:00.773 --> 00:13:02.413
under the auspices of free will,

00:13:02.813 --> 00:13:05.615
convey the word of God on behalf of

00:13:05.654 --> 00:13:07.956
the children of Israel and say to them.

00:13:08.336 --> 00:13:09.876
All right, so this is from Yahowah.

00:13:10.236 --> 00:13:12.038
It's being conveyed to Moshe.

00:13:12.118 --> 00:13:14.359
We take it on the highest authority.

00:13:14.859 --> 00:13:15.559
And he's saying,

00:13:16.399 --> 00:13:19.822
you have the opportunity to choose to

00:13:19.902 --> 00:13:21.042
accept this or reject it.

00:13:21.062 --> 00:13:22.582
It's under the auspices of free will.

00:13:23.547 --> 00:13:26.509
and that it is offered on behalf of

00:13:26.769 --> 00:13:28.890
God to the children of Israel,

00:13:28.951 --> 00:13:30.692
those who engage and endure with God.

00:13:31.033 --> 00:13:34.455
He wanted Moshe to convey the following to

00:13:34.495 --> 00:13:34.754
them.

00:13:35.096 --> 00:13:35.676
The Mowedym,

00:13:36.596 --> 00:13:39.099
these restoring witnesses to the eternal

00:13:40.038 --> 00:13:42.020
testimony regarding the appointed meeting

00:13:42.081 --> 00:13:46.063
times of Yahowah, not of Jews,

00:13:47.325 --> 00:13:50.106
not of a church, of Yahowah.

00:13:51.431 --> 00:13:52.750
are to show the way to the benefits

00:13:52.791 --> 00:13:53.572
of the relationship.

00:13:53.591 --> 00:13:57.472
You are to continually and genuinely take

00:13:57.513 --> 00:13:58.153
advantage of them.

00:13:58.173 --> 00:14:00.453
You're invited to attend them as set

00:14:00.494 --> 00:14:01.573
apart, Miqra'ey,

00:14:01.653 --> 00:14:03.595
invitations to be called out and meet.

00:14:04.575 --> 00:14:06.056
These are my,

00:14:06.096 --> 00:14:08.697
God speaking directly to them, Mowedym,

00:14:08.976 --> 00:14:11.518
eternal witnesses to the restoring

00:14:11.577 --> 00:14:13.857
testimony of these appointed meeting

00:14:13.918 --> 00:14:14.379
times.

00:14:15.339 --> 00:14:18.120
Six days, then,

00:14:19.403 --> 00:14:20.664
the Mala'kah,

00:14:20.784 --> 00:14:23.506
the spiritual messenger will act.

00:14:23.947 --> 00:14:25.448
And then on the seventh day,

00:14:25.509 --> 00:14:27.850
there will be a Shabbat observance,

00:14:28.311 --> 00:14:30.511
a Shabbatown to consider everything

00:14:30.592 --> 00:14:34.254
associated with the promise and purpose of

00:14:34.315 --> 00:14:36.677
the set apart nature of the invitation to

00:14:36.716 --> 00:14:37.618
be called out and meet.

00:14:38.749 --> 00:14:41.830
The spiritual messenger, the Mala'kah,

00:14:42.009 --> 00:14:45.610
which is the full implications of the

00:14:45.650 --> 00:14:47.731
messenger that we discussed in our last

00:14:47.772 --> 00:14:48.251
program,

00:14:48.831 --> 00:14:50.873
is doing everything such that you do not

00:14:50.893 --> 00:14:51.833
have to do anything.

00:14:52.293 --> 00:14:54.394
There are two of them in this case,

00:14:54.794 --> 00:14:57.615
the two men who are presented as the

00:14:57.655 --> 00:14:59.115
greater and lesser luminaries,

00:14:59.216 --> 00:15:02.136
and they are responsible for fulfilling

00:15:02.876 --> 00:15:04.077
the Mowedym.

00:15:04.398 --> 00:15:06.318
And that's why they are mentioned here.

00:15:07.839 --> 00:15:09.720
They're the ones who make the sacrifice.

00:15:09.860 --> 00:15:11.981
They're not asking you to follow them.

00:15:12.022 --> 00:15:13.523
They don't ask you to pick up your

00:15:13.562 --> 00:15:14.082
cross.

00:15:14.123 --> 00:15:16.345
They don't ask you to make any sacrifice.

00:15:16.784 --> 00:15:18.745
They just want you to know,

00:15:18.765 --> 00:15:19.826
and God wants you to know,

00:15:19.886 --> 00:15:22.269
that his spiritual messengers,

00:15:22.609 --> 00:15:24.169
they have done the work.

00:15:24.730 --> 00:15:26.051
And in this case,

00:15:26.130 --> 00:15:27.951
it was Dowd fulfilling Pesach, Matsah,

00:15:27.993 --> 00:15:28.513
and Bikuwrym.

00:15:28.572 --> 00:15:31.715
It will be the one known as Yada,

00:15:31.774 --> 00:15:32.696
the Nakry,

00:15:33.176 --> 00:15:37.119
who will fulfill Shabuwah and Taruwah so

00:15:37.178 --> 00:15:37.399
that,

00:15:38.054 --> 00:15:40.336
Dowd can return with Yahowah on Kipurym,

00:15:40.395 --> 00:15:42.157
and then they will cooperate and

00:15:42.197 --> 00:15:44.517
collaborate again throughout the thousand

00:15:44.557 --> 00:15:45.498
years of Sukah.

00:15:45.898 --> 00:15:47.678
That is who we're talking about as it

00:15:47.719 --> 00:15:50.360
relates to the spiritual messenger who

00:15:50.500 --> 00:15:50.940
works,

00:15:51.340 --> 00:15:53.360
doing everything so that you do not have

00:15:53.400 --> 00:15:54.181
to do anything.

00:15:54.760 --> 00:15:57.142
It is a Shabbat occurrence to approach

00:15:57.182 --> 00:16:00.082
Yahowah, to live and abide throughout time.

00:16:00.984 --> 00:16:04.205
So these godly eternal witnesses to the

00:16:04.245 --> 00:16:06.806
appointed meetings of Yahowah

00:16:07.716 --> 00:16:08.337
are set apart,

00:16:08.357 --> 00:16:09.759
which means they're not religious.

00:16:10.120 --> 00:16:13.203
They're invitations to be called out and

00:16:13.244 --> 00:16:13.524
meet,

00:16:14.044 --> 00:16:15.846
which to receive the benefits of the

00:16:15.886 --> 00:16:18.450
relationship, you're invited to attend,

00:16:18.610 --> 00:16:19.951
to be called out and welcomed.

00:16:20.452 --> 00:16:24.618
Qara, Miqra'ey, over and over again, Mow'ed,

00:16:24.697 --> 00:16:25.238
Mowedym,

00:16:25.859 --> 00:16:29.740
God is reinforcing a very direct concept.

00:16:30.360 --> 00:16:33.062
And here it is, Miqra'ey, Asher, Qara,

00:16:33.701 --> 00:16:35.322
and then Mow'ed.

00:16:35.863 --> 00:16:38.724
There are restoring witnesses to the

00:16:38.764 --> 00:16:41.105
appointed meeting times where you are

00:16:41.264 --> 00:16:45.426
invited and called out to so that you

00:16:45.466 --> 00:16:48.868
can meet and be welcomed into God's

00:16:48.908 --> 00:16:49.248
company.

00:16:51.828 --> 00:16:52.789
In the first month,

00:16:53.309 --> 00:16:54.812
on the fourteenth of the month,

00:16:55.371 --> 00:16:57.313
for the purpose of understanding,

00:16:57.394 --> 00:16:59.375
at twilight, of course, is Passover,

00:16:59.436 --> 00:17:00.537
according to Yahowah.

00:17:01.037 --> 00:17:03.799
And during the fifteenth day of this same

00:17:03.840 --> 00:17:06.701
month is the festival feast of unyeasted

00:17:06.761 --> 00:17:08.022
bread, of Matsah,

00:17:09.064 --> 00:17:11.205
which is necessary to approach Yahowah.

00:17:11.707 --> 00:17:15.250
Seven days you should eat bread without

00:17:15.789 --> 00:17:18.673
the embittering nature of yeast.

00:17:20.028 --> 00:17:21.349
The first and foremost,

00:17:21.390 --> 00:17:24.192
the primary day exists as a set apart

00:17:24.332 --> 00:17:27.673
and cleansing invitation to be called out

00:17:27.733 --> 00:17:30.936
and meet for you to approach and you

00:17:30.957 --> 00:17:34.038
shall not consistently perform any of the

00:17:34.078 --> 00:17:36.840
duties of that spiritual messenger,

00:17:36.881 --> 00:17:37.540
the Mala'kah,

00:17:38.541 --> 00:17:41.804
which is designated as the work of God

00:17:41.844 --> 00:17:46.106
collaborating with these messengers.

00:17:46.147 --> 00:17:48.970
So now approach and come near, be present.

00:17:49.775 --> 00:17:51.895
with this feminine manifestation of God's

00:17:51.935 --> 00:17:54.278
fiery light to near Yahowah,

00:17:55.178 --> 00:17:58.641
to approach Yahowah for seven days,

00:17:59.040 --> 00:18:00.162
to be in God's presence,

00:18:00.182 --> 00:18:02.002
which means you need to be transformed,

00:18:02.262 --> 00:18:04.984
which is the whole nature of approaching

00:18:05.045 --> 00:18:08.707
the fire, which transforms, elevates,

00:18:08.747 --> 00:18:11.788
if you will, decaying organic matter,

00:18:12.009 --> 00:18:13.910
turning it into light and energy.

00:18:14.730 --> 00:18:15.612
On the seventh day,

00:18:15.632 --> 00:18:17.613
there is a set-apart invitation to be

00:18:17.653 --> 00:18:18.733
called out and meet.

00:18:19.736 --> 00:18:22.017
You should not do any part of the

00:18:22.057 --> 00:18:25.376
ministerial responsibilities of heaven's

00:18:26.196 --> 00:18:28.038
messenger, the Mala'kah.

00:18:28.637 --> 00:18:30.377
God's very serious about this.

00:18:30.959 --> 00:18:31.138
Well,

00:18:31.219 --> 00:18:34.578
then that leads to this point as we

00:18:34.679 --> 00:18:37.000
approach the purpose of Bikuwrym.

00:18:37.680 --> 00:18:38.400
Then again,

00:18:38.720 --> 00:18:40.780
Yahowah spoke to Moshe to convey...

00:18:41.912 --> 00:18:42.511
The following,

00:18:42.551 --> 00:18:45.213
speak to the children of Yisrael and say

00:18:45.294 --> 00:18:46.875
to them, indeed,

00:18:46.954 --> 00:18:50.416
when you arrive and enter into the land,

00:18:50.517 --> 00:18:52.498
which for the benefit of the relationship,

00:18:52.998 --> 00:18:56.019
I am giving to you and reap its

00:18:56.059 --> 00:18:56.559
harvest,

00:18:57.220 --> 00:19:00.422
bring a sheath of grain ready for

00:19:00.481 --> 00:19:01.982
transport, an omar,

00:19:02.002 --> 00:19:05.924
and make that sheath of grain that is

00:19:05.984 --> 00:19:08.527
ready for transport to be a first fruits,

00:19:08.987 --> 00:19:10.347
to be resheathed.

00:19:11.198 --> 00:19:16.159
of your harvest, Qatsyr, to the priest,

00:19:16.239 --> 00:19:16.778
the Cohen,

00:19:17.400 --> 00:19:19.740
who was going to officiate so that he

00:19:19.759 --> 00:19:21.580
can explain the purpose of all of this.

00:19:22.500 --> 00:19:24.280
This would be Qara called out,

00:19:25.001 --> 00:19:26.402
never should have been called Leviticus,

00:19:26.422 --> 00:19:27.122
23:10.

00:19:28.321 --> 00:19:29.863
So now that we have been freed from

00:19:29.883 --> 00:19:31.762
the consequence and penalty of our

00:19:31.823 --> 00:19:34.503
propensity to rebel as a result of

00:19:34.564 --> 00:19:35.983
Passover and on yeasted bread,

00:19:36.064 --> 00:19:37.664
our souls are prepared

00:19:38.479 --> 00:19:42.303
for the Bikuwrym harvest we're going home

00:19:43.143 --> 00:19:45.164
but not just to any home as a

00:19:45.224 --> 00:19:51.111
result of becoming immortal and not guilty

00:19:51.211 --> 00:19:53.153
sons and daughters within the covenant

00:19:53.173 --> 00:19:55.494
family we're headed to the promised land

00:19:55.515 --> 00:19:57.576
to live with Yahowah

00:19:58.819 --> 00:20:01.381
with the exception of Chanowk,

00:20:01.520 --> 00:20:04.403
known as Enoch, and ElYah, known as Elijah,

00:20:04.803 --> 00:20:06.663
who were called home long ago.

00:20:07.304 --> 00:20:09.085
It is reasonable to think that the souls

00:20:09.125 --> 00:20:10.885
of many others who accepted Yahowah's

00:20:10.925 --> 00:20:14.167
provision between Adam and Abraham,

00:20:14.248 --> 00:20:16.769
and those who embraced Yah's covenant

00:20:16.808 --> 00:20:19.869
relationship between Abraham and Moshe,

00:20:21.030 --> 00:20:22.852
and from Moshe to Dowd,

00:20:22.932 --> 00:20:24.633
were gathered together

00:20:25.333 --> 00:20:27.153
and taken to Shamaym,

00:20:27.273 --> 00:20:30.153
advanced in terms of their dimensionality,

00:20:30.894 --> 00:20:33.575
during the celebration of firstborn

00:20:33.615 --> 00:20:36.175
children in year four thousand, yeah,

00:20:36.215 --> 00:20:37.096
thirty-three CE.

00:20:38.195 --> 00:20:40.876
And while I suppose it is also possible

00:20:40.916 --> 00:20:43.037
that they will be included in the next

00:20:43.077 --> 00:20:44.178
harvest on Shabuwah,

00:20:44.857 --> 00:20:48.398
when many Gowy and Yahuwdym would join them,

00:20:49.335 --> 00:20:52.375
Since it is categorized as standing grain,

00:20:52.876 --> 00:20:56.157
I suspect that it is of living souls

00:20:56.739 --> 00:20:59.539
who will be withdrawn at that time.

00:21:00.941 --> 00:21:03.981
And that everyone prior to that time will

00:21:04.001 --> 00:21:07.163
have benefited already from the harvest of

00:21:07.183 --> 00:21:07.584
Bikuwrym.

00:21:11.086 --> 00:21:11.768
So similarly,

00:21:12.528 --> 00:21:14.691
since the ripe olives are being picked

00:21:14.770 --> 00:21:17.594
from the tree's branches and not from the

00:21:17.634 --> 00:21:18.055
ground,

00:21:18.535 --> 00:21:21.959
the Taruwah gleaning will be of Jews and

00:21:22.239 --> 00:21:22.900
Israelites.

00:21:22.960 --> 00:21:27.865
These celebrations will be followed,

00:21:27.945 --> 00:21:28.445
I should say,

00:21:28.465 --> 00:21:29.907
by the homecoming on Kipurym.

00:21:31.038 --> 00:21:31.198
Anyway,

00:21:31.218 --> 00:21:33.420
this next statement confirms as much,

00:21:33.640 --> 00:21:37.123
adding the realization that our approval

00:21:37.182 --> 00:21:40.185
before God, well, is a favor from God.

00:21:41.086 --> 00:21:41.547
He said,

00:21:42.067 --> 00:21:45.390
and he should lift up and wave that

00:21:45.410 --> 00:21:47.991
which is associated with the sheath of

00:21:48.231 --> 00:21:52.516
prepared grain to approach the presence of

00:21:52.556 --> 00:21:52.976
Yahowah.

00:21:53.616 --> 00:21:56.519
So he should lift up and wave that

00:21:56.538 --> 00:21:58.800
which is associated with this sheath of

00:21:59.121 --> 00:21:59.902
prepared grain

00:22:01.411 --> 00:22:05.173
that which is bundled and ready to be

00:22:05.232 --> 00:22:08.314
processed for the transport,

00:22:08.894 --> 00:22:13.895
to approach the presence of Yahowah for the

00:22:13.996 --> 00:22:16.936
purpose of you being accepted,

00:22:17.917 --> 00:22:21.098
of you being favorably accommodated and

00:22:21.179 --> 00:22:21.759
approved,

00:22:21.778 --> 00:22:24.019
which means there is a test involved here.

00:22:24.780 --> 00:22:25.580
As a result,

00:22:26.421 --> 00:22:29.363
contemplate the consequence of vacillating

00:22:29.502 --> 00:22:29.903
or of

00:22:30.790 --> 00:22:36.201
Delaying on this Shabbat when the priest

00:22:36.240 --> 00:22:38.285
shall raise and now without a priest,

00:22:38.365 --> 00:22:41.570
it's us symbolically raising and waving

00:22:41.632 --> 00:22:41.711
it.

00:22:44.484 --> 00:22:46.946
This presentation of Bikuwrym is markedly

00:22:46.987 --> 00:22:49.929
different than that of Pesach and Matsah,

00:22:50.409 --> 00:22:52.611
even though it is derived from the same

00:22:52.651 --> 00:22:54.853
text as we read the prelude to it.

00:22:55.313 --> 00:22:57.034
Passover and uneastered bread were

00:22:57.654 --> 00:23:00.057
explicitly titled and dated.

00:23:00.817 --> 00:23:02.377
And there is no mention here of the

00:23:02.458 --> 00:23:04.200
name Bikuwrym, firstborn children,

00:23:04.980 --> 00:23:07.501
or of the sixteenth day of the month,

00:23:07.582 --> 00:23:10.144
although Bikuwrym will be clearly

00:23:10.403 --> 00:23:13.467
identified elsewhere and has been up to

00:23:13.507 --> 00:23:13.967
this point.

00:23:15.480 --> 00:23:16.142
Also different,

00:23:16.162 --> 00:23:18.544
Pesach and Matsah were explicitly labeled

00:23:19.144 --> 00:23:22.348
Mow'ed, Miqra'ey, and Chag,

00:23:22.568 --> 00:23:24.069
all three terms applied.

00:23:24.813 --> 00:23:26.673
where Bikuwrym appears to be included

00:23:26.713 --> 00:23:30.055
within the collective depiction of the

00:23:30.194 --> 00:23:32.974
Mow'ed Miqra'ey of Chag Matsah.

00:23:33.635 --> 00:23:35.336
Just like there is a Chag Sukah

00:23:36.016 --> 00:23:40.436
containing the last three of Yahowah's Mow'ed

00:23:40.738 --> 00:23:41.438
and Mowedym,

00:23:42.038 --> 00:23:44.759
there is a Chag Matsah which includes the

00:23:44.898 --> 00:23:45.578
first three.

00:23:47.790 --> 00:23:49.990
And it will be each individual's

00:23:50.030 --> 00:23:52.291
responsibility to ascertain Yahowah's

00:23:52.352 --> 00:23:55.071
testimony on how to carry out these

00:23:55.173 --> 00:23:58.073
instructions regarding Pesach and Matsah,

00:23:58.393 --> 00:24:00.433
but not entirely so with Bikuwrym,

00:24:00.894 --> 00:24:03.693
where the priests were actually asked to

00:24:03.794 --> 00:24:06.694
demonstrate the uplifting wave offering.

00:24:07.154 --> 00:24:08.914
But in this case,

00:24:08.994 --> 00:24:11.536
we don't have any Kohen,

00:24:11.875 --> 00:24:13.955
so all we have is those who will

00:24:13.996 --> 00:24:15.616
minister on behalf of the people

00:24:16.217 --> 00:24:17.376
representing Yahowah.

00:24:18.384 --> 00:24:19.926
Even more significantly,

00:24:20.207 --> 00:24:22.909
the celebrations of Passover and unyeasted

00:24:22.929 --> 00:24:25.612
bread were initiated during the Yatsa

00:24:25.791 --> 00:24:26.333
Exodus,

00:24:26.752 --> 00:24:28.615
while this particular expression was

00:24:28.674 --> 00:24:32.278
scheduled for the arrival in the Promised

00:24:32.318 --> 00:24:32.558
Land.

00:24:35.088 --> 00:24:38.290
Recognizing that the very few of us now,

00:24:38.310 --> 00:24:38.711
of course,

00:24:38.730 --> 00:24:42.094
are farmers and few of us still reside

00:24:42.114 --> 00:24:44.654
within the promised land and that the

00:24:44.694 --> 00:24:47.836
occasion is not dated and that there has

00:24:47.916 --> 00:24:51.539
not been a Kohen priest from the tribe

00:24:51.599 --> 00:24:54.442
of Lowy around to demonstrate how the nowph

00:24:54.602 --> 00:25:00.305
uplifting wave will work now for well over

00:25:00.705 --> 00:25:01.726
twenty centuries.

00:25:03.227 --> 00:25:04.208
What is a person to do?

